name: HTMLModElement
description: The HTMLModElement interface provides special properties (beyond the regular methods and properties available through the HTMLElement interface they also have available to them by inheritance) for manipulating modification elements, that is <del> and <ins>.

members.name: HTMLModElement.cite
members.description: Is a DOMString reflecting the cite HTML attribute, containing a URI of a resource explaining the change.

members.name: HTMLModElement.datetime
members.description: Is a DOMString reflecting the datetime HTML attribute, containing a date-and-time string representing a timestamp for the change.
